# Job Scoring Rubric

Score each job 1–10. Use this breakdown. Customize the title/industry examples and point weights below to match your own target roles and priorities — see `config.json`'s `scoring_weights` section.

## Scoring Criteria

### Title Match (25 pts)
- VP Professional Services / VP Global Operations / VP Customer Success / SVP PS → 25
- VP Service Delivery / VP GRC / VP Risk & Compliance → 23
- Senior Director Professional Services / Senior Director Global Operations / Senior Director CS → 20
- Senior Director GRC / Senior Director Service Delivery → 18
- Director Professional Services / Director Global Operations / Director Customer Success → 15
- Director GRC / Director Service Delivery / Director SAP → 13
- Manager or below → 0 (skip)

### Industry Match (20 pts)
- Enterprise SaaS, Cybersecurity, GRC, ERP, Cloud → 20
- Technology services, IT consulting → 15
- Non-tech enterprise (manufacturing, finance) with large SAP footprint → 10
- Unrelated industry → 0

### Leadership Scope (20 pts)
- Multi-region team (NA + EMEA or APAC), 15+ direct/indirect reports, P&L → 20
- Multi-region OR large team (10+) OR P&L → 15
- Single region, team of 5–10 → 10
- IC or small team, no P&L → 5

### SAP/GRC Relevance (15 pts)
- SAP GRC, S/4HANA, ERP compliance explicitly required → 15
- Enterprise compliance / risk platforms (non-SAP) → 10
- General enterprise software PS → 5
- No relevance → 0

### Global Scope (10 pts)
- Global delivery explicitly mentioned → 10
- EMEA or APAC mentioned → 7
- North America only → 3

### Salary Match (10 pts)
- $225K–$275K+ or "competitive" at VP level → 10
- $175K–$224K → 5
- Below $175K or not listed → 2

## Score Thresholds
- **8–10**: Strong match — generate cover letter, add to tracker as "Priority"
- **6–7**: Good match — add to tracker as "Review", generate cover letter on request
- **4–5**: Weak match — add to tracker as "Low Priority", no cover letter
- **1–3**: Skip — do not add to tracker
